UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
bool u_xlatb11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_20;
float u_xlat22;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat34;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_13.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb11 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb11 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb11 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_2.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_24.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_24.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_24.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_24.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24.x = dot((-u_xlat11.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24.x = u_xlat16_24.x + u_xlat16_24.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_24.xxx) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];

    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat0.xy).x;

    u_xlat0.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;

    u_xlat11.x = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat11.x = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat16_35;

    u_xlat16_15.xyz = min(u_xlat16_15.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xyz;

    u_xlat11.x = clamp(u_xlat11.x, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;

    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;

    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;

    u_xlat16_13.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_13.x);

    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_13.x;

    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat10_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;

    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat6.xy = vec2(u_xlat34) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat6.xy;

    u_xlat34 = u_xlat10_34 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(8) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
float u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
bool u_xlatb12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_19;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_26;
float u_xlat36;
float u_xlat37;
mediump float u_xlat16_38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_14.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb12 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb12 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb12 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_2.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat12.zxy) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat12.zxy) * u_xlat1.yzx;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * u_xlat1.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_26.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyw = u_xlat16_26.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyw = u_xlat16_26.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyw;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyw;
    u_xlat16_26.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_26.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_26.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_26.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot((-u_xlat12.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat0.xx * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_26.x = u_xlat16_4.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_26.x = max(u_xlat16_26.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_26.x = min(u_xlat16_26.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = (-u_xlat16_26.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_26.x;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = textureLod(_MatMap, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_38).xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_26.x * u_xlat16_26.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;

{

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(8) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec2 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
bool u_xlatb11;
mediump float u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_20;
float u_xlat22;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat33;
float u_xlat34;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_13 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_13;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb11 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb11 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb11 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_2.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13 = min(max(u_xlat16_13, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13 = clamp(u_xlat16_13, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_24.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_24.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_24.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_24.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24.x = dot((-u_xlat11.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24.x = u_xlat16_24.x + u_xlat16_24.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_24.xxx) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24.x = abs(u_xlat16_24.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_24.y = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_24.xy = min(u_xlat16_24.xy, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_36 = (-u_xlat16_24.y) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_24.y * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_36 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_36 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_36 = max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_36 = log2(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_36 = exp2(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_36 = exp2(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = min(u_xlat16_36, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_24.y * u_xlat16_24.y;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_37 + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat11.xxx;
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat16_24.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_16 = (-u_xlat16_5.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16 = (-u_xlat16_16) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16 = (-u_xlat16_24.y) + u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_24.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_16 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) + (-u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat11.x * 0.125 + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat22);
    u_xlat7.y = u_xlat11.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat34 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_9.xy = max(u_xlat7.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));

    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_7 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat11.xy);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyw = u_xlat16_9.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;

    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);

    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);

    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat11.x = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat11.x = max(u_xlat11.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat11.x = min(u_xlat11.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.w + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _Emissive;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.www * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;

    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = min(u_xlat16_15.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat11.x = min(max(u_xlat11.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat11.x = clamp(u_xlat11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_13) + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_13);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_13) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13 = min(max(u_xlat16_13, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13 = clamp(u_xlat16_13, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_13) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_13);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_13) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13 = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13 = min(max(u_xlat16_13, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_13;

    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat0.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_24.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_3.x / u_xlat16_35;

    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_13;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13 = min(max(u_xlat16_13, 0.0), 1.0);

#endif
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_13 * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat16_13;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_35 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_13;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = max(u_xlat16_2.xyw, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = min(u_xlat16_2.xyw, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = u_xlat16_2.xyw + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_24.x * u_xlat16_24.x;
    u_xlat22 = log2(u_xlat16_24.x);
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat22 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat22 = exp2(u_xlat22);
    u_xlat22 = (-u_xlat22) + 2.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat22) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 0.959999979);

    u_xlat33 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat34 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat34 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat6.xy = vec2(u_xlat34) * _DigiST1.zw;

    u_xlat16_34 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat6.xy).x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_34 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat33 = (-u_xlat33) + u_xlat34;

#endif

    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat33) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;

    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);

{

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SketchColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
bool u_xlatb11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_20;
float u_xlat22;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_13.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb11 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb11 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb11 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_2.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_24.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_24.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_24.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_24.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_24.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_24.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_24.x = dot((-u_xlat11.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24.x = u_xlat16_24.x + u_xlat16_24.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_24.xxx) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_24.x = abs(u_xlat16_24.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_24.y = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_24.xy = min(u_xlat16_24.xy, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_36 = (-u_xlat16_24.y) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_24.y * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_36 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_36 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_36 = max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_36 = log2(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_36 = exp2(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_36 = exp2(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_36 = min(u_xlat16_36, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_24.y * u_xlat16_24.y;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_37 + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat11.xxx;
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat16_24.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_37;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_16 = (-u_xlat16_5.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(max(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16 = (-u_xlat16_16) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_16 = (-u_xlat16_24.y) + u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_24.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_16 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) * u_xlat16_5.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) + (-u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat11.x * 0.125 + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat22);
    u_xlat7.y = u_xlat11.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat34 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_9.xy = max(u_xlat7.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xy = u_xlat16_9.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_9.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_7 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat11.xy);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyw = u_xlat16_9.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyw;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat11.x = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat11.x = max(u_xlat11.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat11.x = min(u_xlat11.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.w + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _Emissive;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.www * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat7.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = min(u_xlat16_15.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat11.x = min(max(u_xlat11.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat11.x = clamp(u_xlat11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_13.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_13.x);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_36 * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_24.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = log2(u_xlat16_24.x);
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat11.x = exp2(u_xlat11.x);
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat11.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_24.x = (-u_xlat0.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_24.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_24.x = u_xlat16_35 / u_xlat16_24.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_24.x * u_xlat16_13.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_24.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_24.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_24.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_24.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_13.x = min(max(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_13.x = clamp(u_xlat16_13.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_24.x = u_xlat16_13.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_24.x;
    u_xlat16_24.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_24.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat1.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat1.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat16_1.x = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_1.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX

{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];

    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;

UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;

vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
float u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
bool u_xlatb12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_19;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_26;
float u_xlat36;
float u_xlat37;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
mediump float u_xlat16_38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_14.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_14.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb12 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb12 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb12 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_2.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat12.zxy) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat12.zxy) * u_xlat1.yzx;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * u_xlat1.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_26.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyw = u_xlat16_26.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyw = u_xlat16_26.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyw;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyw;
    u_xlat16_26.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_26.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_26.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_26.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot((-u_xlat12.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat0.xx * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_26.x = u_xlat16_4.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_26.x = max(u_xlat16_26.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_26.x = min(u_xlat16_26.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = (-u_xlat16_26.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_26.x;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = textureLod(_MatMap, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_38).xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_26.x * u_xlat16_26.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat16_6.y * u_xlat16_6.y;
    u_xlat16 = u_xlat16_6.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat5 = u_xlat37 * 0.125 + u_xlat16;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat37 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat16);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat37 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat5 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_7.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xy = u_xlat16_7.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_19.xyz = u_xlat16_7.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_19.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_4.z));
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_39 = exp2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = min(u_xlat16_39, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_4.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_42;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_43 = min(max(u_xlat16_43, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_43 = clamp(u_xlat16_43, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_42) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_42) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_26.x) + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat16_26.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat37 * u_xlat37;
    u_xlat16_26.x = u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_26.x = min(max(u_xlat16_26.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_26.x = clamp(u_xlat16_26.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_43) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_26.xxx + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_26.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_26.x = abs(u_xlat16_26.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_26.x = min(u_xlat16_26.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat44 = (-u_xlat16_26.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat44 * u_xlat44;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot((-u_xlat12.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_42)) + (-u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_8.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_38 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_38 = max(u_xlat16_38, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = log2(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_38 = exp2(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_5.www * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_38) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyw = u_xlat16_10.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyw;
    u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_38) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_38 = min(max(u_xlat16_38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_3.x = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_4.w + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_38 = min(max(u_xlat16_38, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_38 = clamp(u_xlat16_38, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_4.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * _Emissive;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_38) * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat1.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;

    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;

#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_14.xxx + u_xlat16_9.xyz;

#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif

    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;

    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_14.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_14.x);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_14.x;
    u_xlat16_38 = (-u_xlat16_26.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = log2(u_xlat16_26.x);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat0.x = exp2(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + 2.0;

    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);

#endif

    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_14.x * u_xlat16_14.x;

    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;

    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);

    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat4.xyz;

    u_xlat36 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat36 = min(u_xlat36, 1.0);
    u_xlat37 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat37 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat36 * u_xlat37 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat37 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat4.xy = vec2(u_xlat37) * _DigiST1.zw;

    u_xlat16_37 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat4.xy).x;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat16_37 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat36 = (-u_xlat36) + u_xlat37;

    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_38) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;

    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
