UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
vec2 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
mediump float u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat22;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
mediump float u_xlat16_26;
float u_xlat33;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot((-u_xlat11.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_34)) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = abs(u_xlat16_34) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);

    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat16_1.y;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat16_1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat11.x * 0.125 + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat22);

#endif
    u_xlat16_12 = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_12;

#ifdef VERTEX

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;

vec4 u_xlat0;

vec4 u_xlat2;

float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump float u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat22;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
mediump float u_xlat16_26;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
float u_xlat39;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0 = max(u_xlat0, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0 = inversesqrt(u_xlat0);
    u_xlat11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot((-u_xlat11.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_34)) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = abs(u_xlat16_34) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_36 = (-u_xlat16_35) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_3 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_3.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_37 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_37 = exp2(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_37 = min(u_xlat16_37, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat11.xxx;
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_15) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_26) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_26 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-u_xlat16_7.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_15) + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat16_1.y;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat16_1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat11.x * 0.125 + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat22);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat11.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat39 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_3 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat11.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_13 = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat16_13 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_13 + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat11.x = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat11.x = max(u_xlat11.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat11.x = min(u_xlat11.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_0.w + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_3.www * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat8.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat8.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = min(u_xlat16_2.xzw, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xzw;
    u_xlat11.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat11.x = min(max(u_xlat11.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat11.x = clamp(u_xlat11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_2.xzw;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xzw * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = log2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat11.x = exp2(u_xlat11.x);
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat11.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat0 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat0) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_23 + u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x / u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_12.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_7.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xzw;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_13) * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0 = min(u_xlat0, 1.0);
    u_xlat6.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat6.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat6.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat16_6 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat6.xy).x;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16_6 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0 = (-u_xlat0) + u_xlat6.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0 = min(max(u_xlat0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0 = clamp(u_xlat0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat0) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;

    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;

    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);

    u_xlat11.x = clamp(u_xlat11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_2.xzw;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xzw * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = log2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat11.x = exp2(u_xlat11.x);
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat11.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat0 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat0) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_23 + u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x / u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_12.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_7.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_7.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xzw;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_13) * u_xlat10_7.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat0 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0 = min(u_xlat0, 1.0);
    u_xlat6.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat6.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat6.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat6.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat6.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat6.xy;
    u_xlat10_6 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat6.xy).x;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat10_6 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0 = (-u_xlat0) + u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat0 = clamp(u_xlat0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat0) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_38;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;

void main()
{

    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat12.zxy) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat12.zxy) * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat12.yzx) * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat10_4.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.xy = u_xlat16_5.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat16_5.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot((-u_xlat12.xyz), u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);

    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat10_3.y + _RoughNessOffset;

    u_xlat16_33 = min(u_xlat16_33, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_38;
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * 6.0;

    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_5.y * u_xlat16_5.y;
    u_xlat14 = u_xlat16_5.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat35 * 0.125 + u_xlat14;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat35 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat14);
    u_xlat7.y = u_xlat35 + 0.125;
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat4 + 0.125;

    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_6.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;

    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_39 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_39 = exp2(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_39 = min(u_xlat16_39, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = u_xlat10_3.x + _MetallicOffset;

    u_xlat16_19 = clamp(u_xlat16_19, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.x = (-u_xlat16_8.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_8.x = (-u_xlat16_8.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_8.x = (-u_xlat16_33) + u_xlat16_8.x;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat16_33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat35 * u_xlat35;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_8.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = clamp(u_xlat16_33, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_4 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_8.xzw = (-u_xlat10_4.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_19) + u_xlat10_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xzw;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = abs(u_xlat16_33) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_33 = min(u_xlat16_33, 1.0);
    u_xlat40 = (-u_xlat16_33) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_19 * u_xlat16_19;
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = dot((-u_xlat12.xyz), u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_19 + u_xlat16_19;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_19)) + (-u_xlat12.xyz);
    u_xlat10_7 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat10_7.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_38 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_38 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_38 = max(u_xlat16_38, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_38 = log2(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_38 = exp2(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_38 = u_xlat16_38 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10_7.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_4.www * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_BumpShine, u_xlat1.xy);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyw = u_xlat16_9.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyw;
    u_xlat16_38 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_38 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_38);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_38) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_11 = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_11 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_11 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat10_3.w + -0.0500000007;
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat10_3.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_11 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat10_1.www * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat2.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xzw;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_0.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_0.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_22 = (-u_xlat16_33) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat35 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat35) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_22 * u_xlat16_33 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat16_22 = u_xlat16_22 / u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_22 * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_22 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_22 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_22;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_22 * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_22 = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_22;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_4.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = max(u_xlat16_0.xzw, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = min(u_xlat16_0.xzw, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xzw + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_11) * u_xlat10_4.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xzw;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = min(u_xlat2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat34 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat34 = min(u_xlat34, 1.0);
    u_xlat35 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat35 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat35 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat35 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat35) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat3.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat10_35 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlat35 = u_xlat10_35 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat34) + u_xlat35;
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat34) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_33) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
mediump float u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat22;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
mediump float u_xlat16_26;
float u_xlat33;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot((-u_xlat11.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_34)) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = abs(u_xlat16_34) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_36 = (-u_xlat16_35) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_3 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_3.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_37 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_37 = exp2(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_37 = min(u_xlat16_37, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat11.xxx;
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_15) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_26) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;

{

{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;

    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
vec3 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_13;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat22;
mediump float u_xlat16_23;
mediump float u_xlat16_26;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyw;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat0 = max(u_xlat0, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0 = inversesqrt(u_xlat0);
    u_xlat11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot((-u_xlat11.xyz), u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_34)) + (-u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = abs(u_xlat16_34) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_34 = min(u_xlat16_34, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_36 = (-u_xlat16_35) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_36;
    u_xlat16_36 = u_xlat16_36 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_3 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_3.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_37 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_37 = u_xlat16_37 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_37 = exp2(u_xlat16_37);
    u_xlat16_37 = min(u_xlat16_37, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat11.xxx;
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_15) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_26) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_26 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-u_xlat16_7.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_15) + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat16_1.y * u_xlat16_1.y;
    u_xlat22 = u_xlat16_1.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat11.x * 0.125 + u_xlat22;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat22);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat11.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat39 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_37) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_3 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat11.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_13 = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat16_13 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_13 + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat11.x = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat11.x = max(u_xlat11.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat11.x = min(u_xlat11.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_0.w + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_3.www * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat8.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat8.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = min(u_xlat16_2.xzw, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xzw;
    u_xlat11.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat11.x = min(max(u_xlat11.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat11.x = clamp(u_xlat11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_2.xzw;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xzw * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = log2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat11.x = exp2(u_xlat11.x);
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat11.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;

    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat0) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_23 + u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x / u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_12.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_7.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xzw;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_13) * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);

    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz / u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = min(u_xlat6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat0 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0 = min(u_xlat0, 1.0);
    u_xlat39 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat39 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat39 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat7.xy = vec2(u_xlat39) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat16_39 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat16_39 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0 = (-u_xlat0) + u_xlat39;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0 = min(max(u_xlat0, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0 = clamp(u_xlat0, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif

    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat0) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

    u_xlat11.x = clamp(u_xlat11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_2.xzw;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xzw * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xzw = u_xlat16_2.xzw + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_37 * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-u_xlat16_34) + 1.0;
    u_xlat11.x = log2(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat11.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat11.x = exp2(u_xlat11.x);
    u_xlat11.x = (-u_xlat11.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat11.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat0 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_23 = (-u_xlat0) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_23 = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_23 + u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x / u_xlat16_23;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_12.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_12.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_7.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_7.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = max(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = min(u_xlat16_1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xzw;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_13) * u_xlat10_7.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz / u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = min(u_xlat6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat0 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat0 = min(u_xlat0, 1.0);
    u_xlat39 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat39 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat39 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat7.xy = vec2(u_xlat39) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat7.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat7.xy;
    u_xlat10_39 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat10_39 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0 = (-u_xlat0) + u_xlat39;
    u_xlat0 = clamp(u_xlat0, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat0) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat11.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;

layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec2 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_28;

bool u_xlatb48;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_51 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_51 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_51);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_51) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat7.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat8.xy,u_xlat8.z);
    u_xlat7.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat8.xy,u_xlat8.z);
    u_xlat7.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat8.xy,u_xlat8.z);
    u_xlat7.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_51 = dot(u_xlat7, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_52 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_51 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_52;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb17 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb17 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb17 = u_xlatb33 || u_xlatb17;
    u_xlat16_51 = (u_xlatb17) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_18.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_52) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_18.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;

    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat33 = min(max(u_xlat33, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

    u_xlat53 = min(max(u_xlat53, 0.0), 1.0);

#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat54 = min(max(u_xlat54, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat54 = clamp(u_xlat54, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat55 = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat24 = u_xlat55 * 0.125 + u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat24 + 0.125;
    u_xlat55 = u_xlat55 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat8.x);
    u_xlat10.y = u_xlat55 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_11.xy = max(u_xlat10.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xy = u_xlat16_11.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_27.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_27.xyz;
    u_xlat55 = (-u_xlat16_57) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_59 = u_xlat55 * u_xlat55;
    u_xlat16_59 = u_xlat16_59 * u_xlat16_59;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat5.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat8.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat5.zxy) + (-u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat55 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat55 = inversesqrt(u_xlat55);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat55) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat5.zxy) * u_xlat8.yzx;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat5.yzx) * u_xlat8.zxy + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat55 = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat55 = inversesqrt(u_xlat55);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat55) * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat8.y = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat8.z = dot((-u_xlat5.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat55 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat55 = inversesqrt(u_xlat55);
    u_xlat8.xy = vec2(u_xlat55) * u_xlat8.xy;
    u_xlat8.xy = u_xlat8.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_12.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_12.x;
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * 6.0;

    u_xlat16_28.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat55 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52 + 1.0;
    u_xlat55 = float(1.0) / u_xlat55;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_28.xyz * vec3(u_xlat55);
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) + u_xlat16_18.xxx;

    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot((-u_xlat5.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x + u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_28.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_18.xxx) + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_28.xyz, u_xlat16_12.x);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_12.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_18.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_18.x = log2(u_xlat16_18.x);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_18.x = exp2(u_xlat16_18.x);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_18.xxx;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat55) * u_xlat16_13.xyz;

    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_0.www * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_51) * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat48 = (-u_xlat53) * u_xlat53 + 1.0;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat53;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x + u_xlat48;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16_52 / u_xlat48;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat48 = min(u_xlat48, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);

    u_xlat16_8 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;

    u_xlat16_14.xyw = u_xlat16_14.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_14.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_14.xyw;

    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_14.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;

    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat16_18.x;

    u_xlat48 = min(u_xlat48, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_1.w + -0.0500000007;

#else

#endif
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * _ShineColor.xyz;

    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);

#endif

    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat16_57) + 1.0;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
