    u_xlat16_11.x = (-u_xlat48) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_11.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x / u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_11.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_11.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_11.x);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_11.x = min(max(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_11.x = clamp(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_18.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_51 * u_xlat16_18.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_51 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_51));
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat53 * u_xlat17 + (-u_xlat53);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat53 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat17 / u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat16_57 * u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat16_57;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16.x + u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_34 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_34);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat16_34 * 0.5;
    u_xlat32 = (-u_xlat54) + 1.0;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat7.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-u_xlat32) * u_xlat48 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_4.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat32 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb48 = !!(u_xlat32<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb48 = u_xlat32<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_11.xy = (bool(u_xlatb48)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat32 + -2.0;
        u_xlat32 = (u_xlatb48) ? u_xlat32 : u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb32 = !!(u_xlat32<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb32 = u_xlat32<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_34 = (u_xlatb32) ? u_xlat16_11.x : u_xlat16_11.y;
        u_xlati32 = int(u_xlat16_34);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati32].xyz;
        u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat48 = max(u_xlat48, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat48);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat49) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat49 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat48);
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat48 = min(max(u_xlat48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat49;
        u_xlat16_34 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati32].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat16_34;
        u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati32].xyz;
        u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat32 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat32 = min(u_xlat32, 1.0);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat16.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat32 * u_xlat16.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_0.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat16.x) + u_xlat0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16.x = log2(u_xlat16_57);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat16.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat16.x = exp2(u_xlat16.x);
    u_xlat16.x = (-u_xlat16.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat16.xyz = u_xlat16.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_51 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlati0 = int(u_xlat16_51);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat53 * u_xlat17 + (-u_xlat53);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat53 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat17 / u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_34 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat16_57 * u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat16_57;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat33 * u_xlat16.x + u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16.x = 0.5 / u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat32 = (-u_xlat54) + 1.0;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat7.y * 50.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-u_xlat32) * u_xlat48 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat16_4.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat32 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb48 = u_xlat32<2.0;
        u_xlat16_11.xy = (bool(u_xlatb48)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat32 + -2.0;
        u_xlat32 = (u_xlatb48) ? u_xlat32 : u_xlat1.x;
        u_xlatb32 = u_xlat32<1.0;
        u_xlat16_34 = (u_xlatb32) ? u_xlat16_11.x : u_xlat16_11.y;
        u_xlati32 = int(u_xlat16_34);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).xyz;
        u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat48 = max(u_xlat48, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat48);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat49) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat49 = float(1.0) / u_xlat48;
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).y;
        u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat49;
        u_xlat16_34 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).w;
        u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat16_34;
        u_xlat16_34 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati32).xyz;
        u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
        u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlat16.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat32 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat32 = min(u_xlat32, 1.0);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat16.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat32 * u_xlat16.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat10_0.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat16.x) + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16.x = log2(u_xlat16_57);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat16.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat16.x = exp2(u_xlat16.x);
    u_xlat16.x = (-u_xlat16.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat16.xyz = u_xlat16.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);

    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);

    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;

    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);

    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);

    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);

        u_xlatb27 = u_xlat14<2.0;
        u_xlat16_8.xy = (bool(u_xlatb27)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat40 = u_xlat14 + -2.0;
        u_xlat14 = (u_xlatb27) ? u_xlat14 : u_xlat40;
        u_xlatb14 = u_xlat14<1.0;
        u_xlat16_41 = (u_xlatb14) ? u_xlat16_8.x : u_xlat16_8.y;
        u_xlati14 = int(u_xlat16_41);
        u_xlat5.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati14).xyz;
        u_xlat27 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat27 = max(u_xlat27, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat27);
        u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat5.xyz;
        u_xlat40 = float(1.0) / u_xlat27;
        u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati14).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati14).y;
        u_xlat27 = clamp(u_xlat27, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat40;
        u_xlat16_41 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati14).xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati14).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati14).w;
        u_xlat16_41 = clamp(u_xlat16_41, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * u_xlat16_41;
        u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat16_41;
        u_xlat16_41 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
        u_xlat16_41 = clamp(u_xlat16_41, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati14).xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
        u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlat13.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat26 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat26 = min(u_xlat26, 1.0);
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat13.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat26 * u_xlat13.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat10_0.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat13.x) + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat13.x = log2(u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat13.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat13.x = exp2(u_xlat13.x);
    u_xlat13.x = (-u_xlat13.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;

        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat26 + -2.0;
        u_xlat26 = (u_xlatb39) ? u_xlat26 : u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb26 = !!(u_xlat26<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb26 = u_xlat26<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_28 = (u_xlatb26) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;
        u_xlati26 = int(u_xlat16_28);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati26].xyz;
        u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat39);
        u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat1.xyz;
        u_xlat40 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat39);
        u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat39 = min(max(u_xlat39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat40;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati26].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati26].xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlat13.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat26 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat26 = min(u_xlat26, 1.0);
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat13.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat26 * u_xlat13.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_0.x + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat13.x) + u_xlat0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat13.x = log2(u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat13.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat13.x = exp2(u_xlat13.x);
    u_xlat13.x = (-u_xlat13.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;

    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat10_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat39);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat6.xy).x;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlat44<u_xlat6.z;
    u_xlat6.x = (u_xlatb44) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlat44<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.y = (u_xlatb44) ? 0.0 : 1.0;

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};

UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(8) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
vec4 u_xlat7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat16;
uint u_xlatu16;
float u_xlat17;
bool u_xlatb17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
float u_xlat24;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_27;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_28;
float u_xlat32;
int u_xlati32;
bool u_xlatb32;
float u_xlat33;
bool u_xlatb33;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
float u_xlat48;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
bool u_xlatb48;
float u_xlat49;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
mediump float u_xlat16_51;
mediump float u_xlat16_52;
float u_xlat53;
float u_xlat54;
float u_xlat55;
mediump float u_xlat16_57;
mediump float u_xlat16_59;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_51 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_51 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_51);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_51) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat7.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat8.xy,u_xlat8.z);
    u_xlat7.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat8.xy,u_xlat8.z);
    u_xlat7.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat8.xy,u_xlat8.z);
    u_xlat7.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_51 = dot(u_xlat7, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_52 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_51 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_52;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb17 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb17 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb33 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb33 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb17 = u_xlatb33 || u_xlatb17;
    u_xlat16_51 = (u_xlatb17) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_18.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_52) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_18.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);

    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat48 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat48) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat16_48 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat1.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat17 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat17 = min(u_xlat17, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat17 * u_xlat1.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16_48 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat48 = (-u_xlat1.x) + u_xlat48;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat48 = min(max(u_xlat48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_57);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat48) + 1.0;

    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_18.xyz;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat10_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_51 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_51 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_51);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_51) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat17 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb17 = u_xlat17<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat7.x = (u_xlatb17) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat17 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat8.xy).x;
    u_xlatb17 = u_xlat17<u_xlat8.z;
    u_xlat7.y = (u_xlatb17) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat17 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat8.xy).x;
    u_xlatb17 = u_xlat17<u_xlat8.z;
    u_xlat7.z = (u_xlatb17) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    u_xlat17 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat8.xy).x;
    u_xlatb17 = u_xlat17<u_xlat8.z;
    u_xlat7.w = (u_xlatb17) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_51 = dot(u_xlat7, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_52 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_51 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlatb17 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb33 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb17 = u_xlatb33 || u_xlatb17;
    u_xlat16_51 = (u_xlatb17) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_18.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_52) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x;

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(8) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
uint u_xlatu1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
float u_xlat14;
int u_xlati14;
bool u_xlatb14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat18;
vec2 u_xlat20;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_23;
float u_xlat27;
bool u_xlatb27;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
float u_xlat33;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
uint u_xlatu39;
float u_xlat40;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
bool u_xlatb44;
float u_xlat45;
float u_xlat46;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat39);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat6.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_43 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_43;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb44 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb44 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat39 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = vec2(u_xlat39) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat16_39 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat1.xy).x;
    u_xlat1.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat14 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat14 = min(u_xlat14, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat14 * u_xlat1.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat16_39 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat39 = (-u_xlat1.x) + u_xlat39;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat39 = min(max(u_xlat39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat39) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat10_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat39);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat6.xy).x;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlat44<u_xlat6.z;
    u_xlat6.x = (u_xlatb44) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlat44<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.y = (u_xlatb44) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlat44<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.z = (u_xlatb44) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlat44<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.w = (u_xlatb44) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_43 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlatb44 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlatb44 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_42 = (u_xlatb44) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat10_0.xyz;

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};

UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
uint u_xlatu13;
float u_xlat14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat18;
vec2 u_xlat20;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_23;
float u_xlat26;
int u_xlati26;
bool u_xlatb26;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
float u_xlat33;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
bool u_xlatb39;
float u_xlat40;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
bool u_xlatb44;
float u_xlat45;
float u_xlat46;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat39);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat6.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_43 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_43;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb44 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb44 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlatb44 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_42 = (u_xlatb44) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat10_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat39);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat6.xy).x;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlat44<u_xlat6.z;
    u_xlat6.x = (u_xlatb44) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlat44<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.y = (u_xlatb44) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlat44<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.z = (u_xlatb44) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat7.xy).x;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlat44<u_xlat7.z;
    u_xlat6.w = (u_xlatb44) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_43 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlatb44 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlatb44 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_42 = (u_xlatb44) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat39) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat45);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_47 = abs(u_xlat16_47) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_47 = min(u_xlat16_47, 1.0);
    u_xlat46 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat46 = clamp(u_xlat46, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat7.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat7.x = clamp(u_xlat7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat20.x * 0.125 + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat33);
    u_xlat9.y = u_xlat20.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_10.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xy = u_xlat16_10.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_23.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SketchColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat5.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat3.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat1.y;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat2.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(7) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(8) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
bool u_xlatb0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
float u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
vec3 u_xlat13;
bool u_xlatb13;
vec3 u_xlat14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_16;
float u_xlat17;
float u_xlat18;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_20;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat26;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_28;
mediump float u_xlat16_29;
float u_xlat39;
float u_xlat40;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
mediump float u_xlat16_46;
float u_xlat47;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat1.xy,u_xlat1.z);
    u_xlat0.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_15.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb13 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb13 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb13 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_2.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = (-u_xlat13.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat13.zxy) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat40);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat13.zxy) * u_xlat1.yzx;
    u_xlat4.xyz = (-u_xlat13.yzx) * u_xlat1.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat40);
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_28.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyw = u_xlat16_28.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyw = u_xlat16_28.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyw;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyw;
    u_xlat16_28.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat16_28.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_28.x);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_28.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat4.y = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.z = dot((-u_xlat13.xyz), u_xlat16_6.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xx * u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_28.x = u_xlat16_4.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_28.x = max(u_xlat16_28.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_28.x = min(u_xlat16_28.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_41 = (-u_xlat16_28.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * u_xlat16_28.x;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = textureLod(_MatMap, u_xlat1.xy, u_xlat16_41).xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_28.x * u_xlat16_28.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat16_6.y * u_xlat16_6.y;
    u_xlat5 = u_xlat16_6.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat17 * 0.125 + u_xlat5;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat17 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat5);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat17 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat18 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_7.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xy = u_xlat16_7.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_7.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_4.z));
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_45 = exp2(u_xlat16_45);
    u_xlat16_45 = min(u_xlat16_45, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_4.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_9.x = u_xlat16_46;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_9.x = min(max(u_xlat16_9.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_9.x = clamp(u_xlat16_9.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_46) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_46) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat16_28.x) + u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_46 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_46 = min(max(u_xlat16_46, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_46 = clamp(u_xlat16_46, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = (-u_xlat16_5.xyz) * u_xlat16_9.xxx + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = (-u_xlat4.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_46);

{

#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
