void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat10_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat39);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_42) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat39) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat46 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat46);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat46) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat46 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat46 = clamp(u_xlat46, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_43 = abs(u_xlat16_43) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_43 = min(u_xlat16_43, 1.0);
    u_xlat47 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat47 = clamp(u_xlat47, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat8.x = clamp(u_xlat8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat9.y = u_xlat21.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_10.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xy = u_xlat16_10.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_23.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_23.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 + u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_45)) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_9 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat10_9.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_49 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = max(u_xlat16_49, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_49 = log2(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_49 = exp2(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat10_9.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) + u_xlat16_15.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat47) * u_xlat47 + 1.0;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat47;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat18 * u_xlat18 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_42 / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat18;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat46) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat21.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat10_9 = texture2D(_BumpShine, u_xlat21.xy);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat10_9.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat39) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyw = u_xlat16_11.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyw;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat39 = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat39 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat39 = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 0.0);
    u_xlat39 = min(u_xlat39, 100.0);

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec2 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
vec3 u_xlat13;
uint u_xlatu13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat18;
vec2 u_xlat21;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_23;
float u_xlat26;
int u_xlati26;
bool u_xlatb26;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
float u_xlat34;
float u_xlat39;
bool u_xlatb39;
float u_xlat40;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
float u_xlat46;
float u_xlat47;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat39);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_42) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat39) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat46 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat46);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat46) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat46 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat46 = min(max(u_xlat46, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat46 = clamp(u_xlat46, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_43 = abs(u_xlat16_43) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_43 = min(u_xlat16_43, 1.0);
    u_xlat47 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat47 = min(max(u_xlat47, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat47 = clamp(u_xlat47, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat8.x = min(max(u_xlat8.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat8.x = clamp(u_xlat8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat9.y = u_xlat21.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_10.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xy = u_xlat16_10.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_23.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_23.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 + u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_45)) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_9 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_9.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_49 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = max(u_xlat16_49, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_49 = log2(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_49 = exp2(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) + u_xlat16_15.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat47) * u_xlat47 + 1.0;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat47;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat18 * u_xlat18 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_42 / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat18;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat46) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat21.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_9 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat21.xy);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat39) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyw = u_xlat16_11.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyw;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat39 = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat39 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat39 = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 0.0);
    u_xlat39 = min(u_xlat39, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.w + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.www * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat46);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat39 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_45 = (-u_xlat39) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_45 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x / u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_45 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_45);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_45 = min(max(u_xlat16_45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_45 = clamp(u_xlat16_45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_45 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_4.x));
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat47 * u_xlat44 + (-u_xlat47);
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat13.x * u_xlat47 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat13.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat13.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat44 / u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat46 * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat26 * u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat46 * u_xlat13.x + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_28 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_28);
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat16_28 * 0.5;
    u_xlat26 = (-u_xlat8.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat26 * u_xlat26;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat39 * u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat7.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat26) * u_xlat39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat13.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat16_10.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));

    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)

        u_xlat26 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb39 = !!(u_xlat26<2.0);

        u_xlatb39 = u_xlat26<2.0;
#endif

#else

#endif

        u_xlat39 = min(max(u_xlat39, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat39 = clamp(u_xlat39, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat40;

#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

        u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    }

    u_xlat0.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;

    u_xlat13.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;

    u_xlat26 = min(u_xlat26, 1.0);

    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

    u_xlat13.x = log2(u_xlat16_43);

    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat13.x = log2(u_xlat16_43);
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat13.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat13.x = exp2(u_xlat13.x);
    u_xlat13.x = (-u_xlat13.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat0.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat16;
uint u_xlatu16;
float u_xlat17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
float u_xlat25;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_27;
float u_xlat32;
int u_xlati32;
bool u_xlatb32;
float u_xlat33;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
float u_xlat48;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
bool u_xlatb48;
float u_xlat49;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
mediump float u_xlat16_51;
mediump float u_xlat16_52;
float u_xlat53;
float u_xlat54;
mediump float u_xlat16_55;
float u_xlat56;
mediump float u_xlat16_59;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_51 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_51 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_51);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_51) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_51 = (-u_xlat16_18.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_51 = (-u_xlat16_51) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_18.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat16_51 * u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;

    u_xlat48 = (-u_xlat1.x) + u_xlat48;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat48 = min(max(u_xlat48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = (-u_xlat48) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat10_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_51 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_51 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_51);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_51) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_51 = (-u_xlat16_18.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_51 = (-u_xlat16_51) + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat10_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_18.xxx + u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat16_51 * u_xlat16_51;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_52 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_52 = abs(u_xlat16_52) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_52 = min(u_xlat16_52, 1.0);
    u_xlat53 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat53 = clamp(u_xlat53, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat54 = dot(u_xlat5.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat54 = clamp(u_xlat54, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat56 = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat56 * 0.125 + u_xlat9.x;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat56 = u_xlat56 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat9.x);
    u_xlat10.y = u_xlat56 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_11.xy = max(u_xlat10.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xy = u_xlat16_11.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_27.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_27.xyz;
    u_xlat56 = (-u_xlat16_52) + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat16_55 * u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat5.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat9.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat5.zxy) + (-u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = inversesqrt(u_xlat56);
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat56) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat5.zxy) * u_xlat9.yzx;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat5.yzx) * u_xlat9.zxy + (-u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat10.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = inversesqrt(u_xlat56);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat56) * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat9.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat9.y = dot(u_xlat10.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat9.z = dot((-u_xlat5.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat56 = inversesqrt(u_xlat56);
    u_xlat9.xy = vec2(u_xlat56) * u_xlat9.xy;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
uint u_xlatu1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
float u_xlat14;
int u_xlati14;
bool u_xlatb14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat18;
vec2 u_xlat21;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_23;
float u_xlat27;
bool u_xlatb27;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
float u_xlat34;
float u_xlat39;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
uint u_xlatu39;
float u_xlat40;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
float u_xlat46;
float u_xlat47;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat39 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat39);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_15.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_42) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat39) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat46 = dot(u_xlat8.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
    u_xlat46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat46);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat46) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat46 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat46 = min(max(u_xlat46, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat46 = clamp(u_xlat46, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_43 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_43 = abs(u_xlat16_43) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_43 = min(u_xlat16_43, 1.0);
    u_xlat47 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat47 = min(max(u_xlat47, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat47 = clamp(u_xlat47, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat8.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat8.x = min(max(u_xlat8.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat8.x = clamp(u_xlat8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat9.y = u_xlat21.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_10.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xy = u_xlat16_10.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_23.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_23.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 + u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_45)) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_9 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_9.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_49 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = max(u_xlat16_49, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_49 = log2(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_49 = exp2(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) + u_xlat16_15.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat47) * u_xlat47 + 1.0;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat47;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat18 * u_xlat18 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_42 / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat18;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat46) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat21.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_9 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat21.xy);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);

{

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat10_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;

    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat39);

    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);

    u_xlat46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat46);

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;

    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat18;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;

    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);

    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));

    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat10_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat46 * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43;

    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * vec3(u_xlat40) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_15.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);

    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati39 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)

        u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;

    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;

    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;

};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;

    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;

    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 1.17549435e-38);

    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif

    u_xlat46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat46);

    u_xlat8.x = min(max(u_xlat8.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat8.x = clamp(u_xlat8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat9.x = u_xlat9.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat21.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat9.y = u_xlat21.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_10.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));

    u_xlat16_23.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_23.xyz;
    u_xlat16_45 = dot((-u_xlat1.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 + u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_45)) + (-u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_45;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * 6.0;

    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_9.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_49 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = max(u_xlat16_49, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_49 = log2(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_49 = exp2(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_49 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) + u_xlat16_15.xxx;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_45) * u_xlat9.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat47) * u_xlat47 + 1.0;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat47;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat18 * u_xlat18 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_42 / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat18;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat46) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat21.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_9 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat21.xy);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat39) + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyw = u_xlat16_11.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyw;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat39 = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat39 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat39 = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat39 = max(u_xlat39, 0.0);
    u_xlat39 = min(u_xlat39, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_1.w + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.www * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat39) * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat9.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat46);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;

#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15.x = min(max(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif

    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_45 = min(max(u_xlat16_45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_45;

    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else

#endif

    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;

    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;

    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_4.x));
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat47 * u_xlat44 + (-u_xlat47);
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat47 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat13 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat44 / u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat46 * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat26 * u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat46 * u_xlat13 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_28 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_28);

#endif

    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)

#endif

        u_xlat1.x = u_xlat26 + -2.0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat10_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat10_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_1.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);

#endif
uniform 	vec4 _DigiST1;
uniform 	float _DigiDistore;
uniform 	vec4 _Time;
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MatMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
float u_xlat4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump float u_xlat16_13;
vec3 u_xlat14;
vec3 u_xlat15;
float u_xlat16;
float u_xlat17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
mediump float u_xlat16_21;
float u_xlat27;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
float u_xlat41;
mediump float u_xlat16_44;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
float u_xlat46;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat14.zxy) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = inversesqrt(u_xlat41);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat41) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat14.zxy) * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = inversesqrt(u_xlat41);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat41) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.xy = u_xlat16_5.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_5.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyw = u_xlat16_5.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_5.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyw;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat3.y = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat3.z = dot((-u_xlat14.xyz), u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat2.x);
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xx * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat2.xy = u_xlat2.xy * vec2(0.5, 0.5) + vec2(0.5, 0.5);
    u_xlat16_3 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_39 = u_xlat16_3.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_39 = max(u_xlat16_39, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_39 = min(u_xlat16_39, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_44 = (-u_xlat16_39) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_44;
    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = textureLod(_MatMap, u_xlat2.xy, u_xlat16_44).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(_MatMapMul);
    u_xlat16_45 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_39;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat16_45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat2.xxx;
    u_xlat16 = u_xlat16_5.y * u_xlat16_5.y;
    u_xlat4 = u_xlat16_5.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat17 = u_xlat16 * 0.125 + u_xlat4;
    u_xlat16 = u_xlat16 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat4);
    u_xlat7.y = u_xlat16 + 0.125;
    u_xlat7.x = u_xlat17 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_6.xy = max(u_xlat7.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xy = u_xlat16_6.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_6.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_3.z));
    u_xlat16_8.x = u_xlat16_8.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_8.x = exp2(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.x = min(u_xlat16_8.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xxx;
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat16_3.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_21;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_34 = min(max(u_xlat16_34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_21 = (-u_xlat16_21) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_21 = (-u_xlat16_21) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_21 = (-u_xlat16_39) + u_xlat16_21;
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat16_21 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_21 = min(max(u_xlat16_21, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_21 = clamp(u_xlat16_21, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-u_xlat16_4.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);

    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_0.x);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;

#else
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat40);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat14.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_45 * u_xlat1.x;

    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xzw * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = _SHshadow + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_44 = min(max(u_xlat16_44, 0.0), 1.0);

    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_44) + u_xlat16_0.xzw;

    u_xlat16_44 = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_6.xyz);

    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_39) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

vec4 u_xlat0;

float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Smoothness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissionColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SketchColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}
