UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
float u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat23;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
float u_xlat37;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat1.xy);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_11.x = min(max(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_11.x = clamp(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_0.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12.x = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat12.x * u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat12.x = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat12.x = max(u_xlat12.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat12.x = min(u_xlat12.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.w + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.www * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat4.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_35 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_3.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = (-u_xlat16_15.xyz) * u_xlat16_14.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_41 = dot((-u_xlat5.xyz), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 + u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_41)) + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = abs(u_xlat16_41) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_41 = min(u_xlat16_41, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_35) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat12.x * u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_42 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_5 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = log2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_35 = exp2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_35 = exp2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat4.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat23 = (-u_xlat16_41) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat23 * u_xlat23;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat16_2.y * u_xlat16_2.y;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_2.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat23 * 0.125 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat23 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat6.y = u_xlat23 + 0.125;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat4.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_9.xy = max(u_xlat6.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xy = u_xlat16_9.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_14.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_36 = min(max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_36 = clamp(u_xlat16_36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat12.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat12.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat16_41) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_13.x + u_xlat23;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_24 / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_13.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_15.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_15.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_41 * u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat23 = log2(u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat23 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat23 = exp2(u_xlat23);
    u_xlat23 = (-u_xlat23) + 2.0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat23) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat12.x = min(u_xlat12.x, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat12.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat5.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = texture(_RampTex, u_xlat5.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat34 = min(u_xlat34, 1.0);
    u_xlat37 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat37 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat37 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat37 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat37) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat5.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat16_37 = texture(_ClothTex, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat16_37 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat34) + u_xlat37;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat34 = min(max(u_xlat34, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat34) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;

    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;

    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;

    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat4.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_35 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat10_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_15.xyz = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat10_15.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = (-u_xlat10_15.xyz) * u_xlat16_14.xxx + u_xlat10_15.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_41 = dot((-u_xlat5.xyz), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 + u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_41)) + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = abs(u_xlat16_41) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_41 = min(u_xlat16_41, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_35) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat12.x * u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_42 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_5 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat10_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = log2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_35 = exp2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = log2(abs(u_xlat10_0.z));
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat10_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_35 = exp2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat4.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat23 = (-u_xlat16_41) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat23 * u_xlat23;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat16_2.y * u_xlat16_2.y;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_2.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat23 * 0.125 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat23 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat6.y = u_xlat23 + 0.125;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat4.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_9.xy = max(u_xlat6.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xy = u_xlat16_9.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_14.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = clamp(u_xlat16_36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat12.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat12.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat16_41) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_24 * u_xlat16_13.x + u_xlat23;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_24 / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_13.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat10_15.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_15.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat10_15.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_41 * u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat23 = log2(u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat23 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat23 = exp2(u_xlat23);
    u_xlat23 = (-u_xlat23) + 2.0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat23) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat12.x = min(u_xlat12.x, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat12.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat5.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat10_12.xyz = texture2D(_RampTex, u_xlat5.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat10_12.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * _RampTexColor.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat34 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat34 = min(u_xlat34, 1.0);
    u_xlat37 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat37 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat34 * u_xlat37 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat37 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat37) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat5.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat10_37 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat10_37 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat34) + u_xlat37;
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat34) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;

vec3 u_xlat5;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
float u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat16;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat1.xy);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_11.x = min(max(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_11.x = clamp(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_0.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12.x = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat12.x * u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat12.x = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat12.x = max(u_xlat12.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat12.x = min(u_xlat12.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.w + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.www * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat4.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_35 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_3.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = (-u_xlat16_15.xyz) * u_xlat16_14.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_41 = dot((-u_xlat5.xyz), u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 + u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_41)) + (-u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = abs(u_xlat16_41) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_41 = min(u_xlat16_41, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_35) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_42 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_5 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = log2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_35 = exp2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_35 = exp2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat4.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat4.x = (-u_xlat16_41) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat4.x * u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat16_2.y * u_xlat16_2.y;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_2.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat16 = u_xlat4.x * 0.125 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat4.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat5.x);
    u_xlat6.y = u_xlat4.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat16 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_9.xy = max(u_xlat6.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xy = u_xlat16_9.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_14.xyz + u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_36 = min(max(u_xlat16_36, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_36 = clamp(u_xlat16_36, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat16_41) + 1.0;
    u_xlat12.x = log2(u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat12.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat12.x = exp2(u_xlat12.x);
    u_xlat12.x = (-u_xlat12.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_24 + u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x / u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_13.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif

    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat16_41) + 1.0;
    u_xlat12.x = log2(u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat12.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat12.x = exp2(u_xlat12.x);
    u_xlat12.x = (-u_xlat12.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_24 + u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_13.x / u_xlat16_24;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_13.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat10_15.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_15.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat10_15.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat4.x = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat4.x + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat4.x + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat4.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat4.xy = u_xlat4.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat4.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat4.xy;
    u_xlat10_4 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat4.xy).x;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat10_4 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat1.x) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"

UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;

vec3 u_xlat14;
vec3 u_xlat15;
float u_xlat16;
float u_xlat17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
mediump float u_xlat16_21;
float u_xlat27;
mediump float u_xlat16_31;
mediump float u_xlat16_34;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
float u_xlat41;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_44;
mediump float u_xlat16_45;
float u_xlat46;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat14.zxy) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = inversesqrt(u_xlat41);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat41) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat14.zxy) * u_xlat2.yzx;

#ifdef VERTEX

{

    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].zxy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_CameraToWorld[1].yzx * (-u_xlat14.zxy) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = inversesqrt(u_xlat41);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat41) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat14.zxy) * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-u_xlat14.yzx) * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = inversesqrt(u_xlat41);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat41) * u_xlat3.xyz;

    u_xlat16 = u_xlat16 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat4);

    u_xlat16_8.x = exp2(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.x = min(u_xlat16_8.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xxx;
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat10_3.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_21;
    u_xlat16_34 = clamp(u_xlat16_34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_21 = (-u_xlat16_21) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_21 = (-u_xlat16_21) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_21 = (-u_xlat16_39) + u_xlat16_21;
    u_xlat16_21 = u_xlat16_21 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_21 = clamp(u_xlat16_21, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_4 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = (-u_xlat10_4.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_34) + u_xlat10_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = (-u_xlat3.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_21);
    u_xlat16_21 = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat16_21 = abs(u_xlat16_21) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_21 = min(u_xlat16_21, 1.0);
    u_xlat46 = (-u_xlat16_21) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat46 * u_xlat46;
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 * u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_34) * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_34 = dot((-u_xlat14.xyz), u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_34 = u_xlat16_34 + u_xlat16_34;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_34)) + (-u_xlat14.xyz);

    u_xlat16_44 = u_xlat16_44 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;

    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;

    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-u_xlat14.xyz) + u_xlat15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_4.www * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;

    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);

    u_xlat16_11.xyw = u_xlat16_11.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyw;
    u_xlat16_44 = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);

    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_13 = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat16_13 * u_xlat16_13 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_13 + 1.0;
    u_xlat40 = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;

    u_xlat40 = max(u_xlat40, 0.0);
    u_xlat40 = min(u_xlat40, 100.0);

    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13 = u_xlat10_3.w * _EmisssionScale;

    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xxx * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat10_2.www * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = inversesqrt(u_xlat40);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat1.xyz;

    u_xlat14.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;

    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_45 / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat16_39 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.z = u_xlat16_39 + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xz = u_xlat1.xz * u_xlat1.xz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = clamp(u_xlat41, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat1.xyw * vec3(u_xlat41);
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = vec3(u_xlat41) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat1.xyw * _SpecularColor.xyz;

    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat1.xyw * _MainLightColor.www;

    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xzw * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_44 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_44);

    u_xlat16_44 = clamp(u_xlat16_44, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xzw * u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = max(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = min(u_xlat16_6.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xzw + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_44 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_44 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_44);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_44) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_6.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_8.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-u_xlat16_21) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = log2(u_xlat16_21);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat1.x = exp2(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat1.x) + 2.0;
    u_xlat1.xyw = u_xlat1.xxx * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat1.z * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_31 = (-u_xlat1.z) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_31 = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_31 + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x / u_xlat16_31;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_5.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_18.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = clamp(u_xlat16_5.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_5.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_5.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat10_4.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_4.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xxx;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xzw = u_xlat16_0.xzw + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_13) * u_xlat10_4.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xzw;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = min(u_xlat2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat27 = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat27 = min(u_xlat27, 1.0);
    u_xlat41 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat41 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat27 * u_xlat41 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat41 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat41) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat3.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat10_41 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat3.xy).x;
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat10_41 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat27 = (-u_xlat27) + u_xlat41;
    u_xlat27 = clamp(u_xlat27, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat27) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat27) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyw * vec3(u_xlat16_39) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _RampTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
float u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat23;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
float u_xlat34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
float u_xlat37;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat1.xy);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_11.x = min(max(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_11.x = clamp(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_0.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12.x = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat12.x * u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat12.x = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;

SubProgram "gles " {

"// hash: ccd83acb9b2da7a0
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _FurTilling;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
mediump float u_xlat16_0;

void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_0 * u_xlat16_0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_BumpShine, u_xlat1.xy);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;

    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);

    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_11.x = clamp(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_0 = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_0 + 1.0;

    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_0 * u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat12.x = max(u_xlat12.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat12.x = min(u_xlat12.x, 100.0);

    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);

    u_xlat16_2.xyw = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;

    u_xlat4.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat4.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_35 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat10_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_3.x;

    u_xlat16_14.xyz = (-u_xlat10_15.xyz) * u_xlat16_14.xxx + u_xlat10_15.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);

    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;

    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;

    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.75 + 0.25;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;

    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 + u_xlat16_41;

    u_xlat16_41 = abs(u_xlat16_41) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_41 = min(u_xlat16_41, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = (-u_xlat16_35) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_42;

    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat12.x * u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_42 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_5 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat10_5.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_35 = log2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_35 = exp2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10_5.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35);

    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat10_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_35 = exp2(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat4.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat23 = (-u_xlat16_41) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat23 * u_xlat23;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat16_2.y * u_xlat16_2.y;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_2.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat23 * 0.125 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat23 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat6.y = u_xlat23 + 0.125;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat4.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_9.xy = max(u_xlat6.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xy = u_xlat16_9.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_9.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_14.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xxx + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = clamp(u_xlat16_36, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_36 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_36 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_36);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_36) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat12.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-u_xlat12.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_24 = (-u_xlat16_41) + 1.0;

    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_13.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;

    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_13.x * u_xlat16_2.x;

    u_xlat16_13.x = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_13.x;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat10_15.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_15.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat10_15.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_41 * u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat23 = log2(u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat23 = u_xlat23 * _DigiPow;
    u_xlat23 = exp2(u_xlat23);
    u_xlat23 = (-u_xlat23) + 2.0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat23) * _DigiBaseColor0.xyz;
    u_xlat12.x = min(u_xlat12.x, 0.959999979);
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat12.x * _RampTex_ST.x + _RampTex_ST.z;
    u_xlat5.y = 0.0;
    u_xlat10_12.xyz = texture2D(_RampTex, u_xlat5.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat10_12.xyz;

    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1 = min(u_xlat1, vec4(100.0, 100.0, 100.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat37 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat37 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat1.w * u_xlat37 + _DigiBaseColor0.w;
    u_xlat37 = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat5.xy = vec2(u_xlat37) * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat5.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat5.xy;
    u_xlat10_37 = texture2D(_ClothTex, u_xlat5.xy).x;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat10_37 + vs_TEXCOORD0.y;
    u_xlat34 = (-u_xlat34) + u_xlat37;
    u_xlat34 = clamp(u_xlat34, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat34) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat34) + 1.0;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat4.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;

UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.x = fract(_Time.x);
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xx * _DigiST1.zw;
    u_xlat0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _DigiST1.xy + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(_ClothTex, u_xlat0.xy, 0.0).z;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_DigiDistore, _DigiDistore, _DigiDistore));
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.200000003, 0.200000003, 0.200000003) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _ClothTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpShine;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec3 u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
float u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
float u_xlat16;
mediump float u_xlat16_24;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_36;
float u_xlat37;
mediump float u_xlat16_37;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = _ShineRoughness * _ShineRoughness;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat1.xy = vs_TEXCOORD0.xy * vec2(vec2(_ShineScale, _ShineScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_BumpShine, u_xlat1.xy);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
    u_xlat16_2.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_2.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_2.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_11.x = min(max(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_11.x = clamp(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_11.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_0.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat12.x = _ShineRoughness / u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat12.x * u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat12.x = _ShineRoughness * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat12.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat12.x = max(u_xlat12.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat12.x = min(u_xlat12.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.w + -0.0500000007;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _ShineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_1.www * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * vec3(1.05299997, 1.05299997, 1.05299997);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = u_xlat16_2.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat16_2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_2.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat4.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_35 = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_35 = min(u_xlat16_35, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_3.x / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat4.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat4.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat4.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_35 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat15;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_14.x = u_xlat16_3.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_14.x = min(max(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_14.x = clamp(u_xlat16_14.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);

{

    u_xlat12.xyz = u_xlat12.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;

    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_2.xyz;

    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat1.x = max(_DigiChange, -1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat37 = _DigiBaseColor1.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat37 = u_xlat37 + (-_DigiBaseColor0.w);

    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat4.xyz;

    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat12.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_35) + u_xlat16_2.xyz;

}
